After all, that is most of us.
Some have a too short neck, the others a too young figure without neat curves and still others are fluffy.
It is up to the stylist to visually conceal wide shoulders, lengthen the neck or highlight the necessary curves.
We also got tips on how to dress a woman like Jennifer Lopez - that is, with a large bust, wide hip and narrow waist - pretty and figure-emphasized without being too provocative.
For example, if the difference between waist and hips is so big that the skirt or pants really don't fit, you should at least have a piece tailored to fit.
You will not regret this, because well-fitting clothing is simply priceless.
