How to unmask a lie
A look at the current headlines shows how worrying and widespread deception and lies are in everyday life.
The Republican presidential candidate, Herman Cain, is obsessed with the accusations of sexual harassment by several women, and both sides accuse each other of lying.
The leadership of Penn State is accused of mistreatment for allegedly withholding reports that a retired football coach sexually abused boys.
